para.tab:
(

 a

) A Selection Committee, to consist of the Deputy Speaker, the Government Whip, the Opposition Whip, the Third Party Whip, 4 Government members, and 3 Opposition or other non-government members, shall be appointed at the commencement of each Parliament to arrange the timetable and order of business for private Members' business and committee and delegation reports on each sitting Monday pursuant to standing order 101.

